{
  "stem": "311.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they're quite-- for a secondary operation, they may be-- they're much better than the power presses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so if you do it with your hand, and it caught it here, you're not going to chop your fingers off.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- well, we had to set-- set up something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to make a living.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we set up a-- a-- a shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we had a couple, from our workers, Polish guys, come in to, you know, to work in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they came for a whole week, slept over, and they went home on Friday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was the-- a reverse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They worked till they say, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They saw what's going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They say, no more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They stopped-- they stopped coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while they were coming in, they were bringing food and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But since we were doing for outside work, we had-- everybody had a Kennkarte, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a yellow card with your picture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was monthly stamped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I remember, I used to go to go and get it stamped in-- you know, by the SS, you know, the Totenkopf Regiment, whatever it is-- for me, for my father, and for the two Polacks who used to come in.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were the reverse cards, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And even if they didn't work, I keep on going this way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a important thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, it was a still important business, even we did a-- a minimum, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I had-- first of all, I had the freedom to go out, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I shouldn't go with-- with the the arm band.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The yellow star?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
